      <title>债务刹车限制选项，德国联合政府接近达成预算协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/german-coalition-nears-budget-deal-as-debt-brake-limits-options</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的执政联盟最早将于周五提交一份预算草案，旨在通过增加基础设施和国防支出，同时遵守债务限制，来结束政治内斗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/german-coalition-nears-budget-deal-as-debt-brake-limits-options</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>最高法院任期即将结束，避免审理新的枪支案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/supreme-court-sidesteps-new-gun-cases-as-it-closes-out-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院选择不将任何新的枪支权利案件添加到秋季议程中，以避免在法官九个月任期即将结束时出现大量有关宪法第二修正案的上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/supreme-court-sidesteps-new-gun-cases-as-it-closes-out-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:48:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及政府改组将任命库乔克为财政部长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/egypt-to-name-kouchouk-as-finance-minister-extranews-reports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据 Extranews 报道，埃及即将任命艾哈迈德·库舒克为该国自 2018 年以来首位新任财政部长，目前这个北非国家正在摆脱几十年来最严重的经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/egypt-to-name-kouchouk-as-finance-minister-extranews-reports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:37:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>色情网站年龄验证法将接受最高法院审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/porn-site-age-verification-law-will-get-supreme-court-scrutiny</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院将仔细审查德克萨斯州的一项法律，该法律要求色情网站核实用户的年龄，并同意听取行业贸易集团的论点，即该措施侵犯了成年人的宪法权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/porn-site-age-verification-law-will-get-supreme-court-scrutiny</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:34:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FDA 遏制调味型电子烟的努力引起最高法院审查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/fda-efforts-to-curb-flavored-vapes-draw-supreme-court-review</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国最高法院表示，将听取拜登政府的上诉，旨在加强食品药品管理局禁止可能对儿童有吸引力的调味型电子烟产品的权力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/fda-efforts-to-curb-flavored-vapes-draw-supreme-court-review</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:32:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被谋杀候选人的竞选搭档在厄瓜多尔选举中与诺沃亚对决</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ecuador-violence-andrea-gonzalez-challenges-president-daniel-noboa-in-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[遇害的总统候选人费尔南多·比亚维森西奥的竞选搭档现在请求选民委托她带领厄瓜多尔走出自去年他遇害以来一直受到全球关注的暴力危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/ecuador-violence-andrea-gonzalez-challenges-president-daniel-noboa-in-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞争夺多数席位，法国竞争对手纷纷拉拢候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-seeks-broad-support-to-win-french-parliamentary-majority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[玛丽娜·勒庞正在寻求极右翼国民联盟党以外的支持，以便即使她未能获得绝对多数票也能执政，因为主流政党已将候选人从周日的决选中撤出，以阻止她执政。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/le-pen-seeks-broad-support-to-win-french-parliamentary-majority</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克在最后一搏选举中增加恐惧因素</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/sunak-ramps-up-the-fear-factor-in-frantic-final-uk-election-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工党领袖基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 认为，里希·苏纳克 (Rishi Sunak) 的最后一搏是“绝望的”，旨在煽动人们对反对党将在周四的英国大选中赢得绝对多数席位的担忧，而首相的竞选活动变得越来越疯狂，因为它试图避免保守党的惨败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/sunak-ramps-up-the-fear-factor-in-frantic-final-uk-election-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:00:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管鲁托保证，肯尼亚反政府抗议活动仍继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/death-toll-in-kenyan-anti-government-protests-at-39-group-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，肯尼亚多个城市再次爆发反政府示威活动，抗议者呼吁严厉打击政府腐败和浪费性政府开支。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/death-toll-in-kenyan-anti-government-protests-at-39-group-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 05:52:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>奥尔班首次访问基辅，与泽连斯基一起游说停火</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/orban-to-make-kyiv-visit-amid-fraught-ukraine-ties-reports-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自俄罗斯入侵以来，匈牙利总理维克托·奥尔班首次访问基辅，敦促乌克兰总统弗拉基米尔·泽连斯基考虑停火，这暴露了两国领导人之间的深刻分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/orban-to-make-kyiv-visit-amid-fraught-ukraine-ties-reports-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 05:41:38 GMT</pubDate>
